  "fullOutput": "<path>/home/anmol/Projects/experiments/dhvaniportfolio-/index.html</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: <!DOCTYPE html>\n2: <html lang=\"en\">\n3: <head>\n4: <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n5: <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n6: <title>Dhvani Chauhan — Graphic Design</title>\n7: <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\n8: <link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\n9: <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,300..700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n10: <style>\n11:   :root{\n12:     --paper:#FAF8F5;\n13:     --panel:#F2EFEA;\n14:     --ink:#1E1C1A;\n15:     --ink-soft:#5A5550;\n16:     --line:#DDD7CD;\n17:     --accent:#A8443A;\n18:     --accent-soft:#E8D9D2;\n19:     --num-offset:52px;\n20:   }\n21: \n22:   *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}\n23:   html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}\n24: \n25:   body{\n26:     background:var(--paper);\n27:     color:var(--ink);\n28:     font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;\n29:   }\n30: \n31:   @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){\n32:     *{animation:none !important; transition:none !important;}\n33:   }\n34: \n35:   a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none;}\n36:   img{display:block;max-width:100%;}\n37: \n38:   .wrap{max-width:1160px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 40px;}\n39: \n40:   nav{\n41:     position:sticky; top:0; z-index:50;\n42:     background:var(--paper);\n43:     border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);\n44:   }\n45:   nav .wrap{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:72px;}\n46:   .brand{\n47:     font-family:'Fraunces', serif;\n48:     font-weight:500;\n49:     font-size:1.15rem;\n50:     letter-spacing:0.01em;\n51:     text-transform:uppercase;\n52:   }\n53:   .brand span{color:var(--accent);}\n54:   .navlinks{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:36px;font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.04em;text-transform:uppercase;}\n55:   .navlinks a{position:relative;padding:6px 0;color:var(--ink-soft);transition:color .2s;}\n56:   .navlinks a:hover{color:var(--ink);}\n57:   .navlinks a:focus-visible, .btn:focus-visible, .pcard a:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--accent); outline-offset:3px;}\n58:   .nav-resume{\n59:     border:1.5px solid var(--ink); color:var(--ink) !important;\n60:     padding:9px 18px !important; transition:background .2s, color .2s, border-color .2s;\n61:   }\n62:   .nav-resume:hover{background:var(--ink); color:var(--paper) !important;}\n63: \n64:   header.hero{border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}\n65:   .hero-main{padding:100px 0 80px;}\n66: \n67:   .eyebrow{\n68:     font-size:0.78rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase;\n69:     color:var(--accent); margin-bottom:20px; display:block;\n70:   }\n71: \n72:   h1.title{\n73:     font-family:'Fraunces', serif;\n74:     font-weight:400;\n75:     font-size:clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem);\n76:     line-height:1.08;\n77:     letter-spacing:-0.01em;\n78:     max-width:780px;\n79:   }\n80:   h1.title em{\n81:     font-style:italic; font-weight:500; color:var(--accent);\n82:   }\n83: \n84:   .hero-sub{\n85:     max-width:680px; margin-top:24px;\n86:     font-size:1rem; line-height:1.7; color:var(--ink-soft);\n87:   }\n88: \n89:   .hero-stats{\n90:     display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4, 1fr);\n91:     margin-top:48px; border-top:1px solid var(--line);\n92:   }\n93:   .side-stat{border-right:1px solid var(--line); padding:20px 28px 0 0;}\n94:   .side-stat:last-child{border-right:none;}\n95:   .side-stat .label{font-size:0.72rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--ink-soft); display:block; margin-bottom:6px;}\n96:   .side-stat .value{font-size:0.98rem; font-weight:600;}\n97: \n98:   .section{padding:88px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}\n99:   .section-head{\n100:     display:flex; align-items:baseline; gap:14px; margin-bottom:56px; flex-wrap:wrap;\n101:   }\n102:   .section-head-text{flex:1; min-width:240px;}\n103:   .section-num{\n104:     font-family:'Fraunces', serif; font-weight:400; font-style:italic; font-size:1.4rem; color:var(--accent);\n105:     line-height:1;\n106:   }\n107:   h2.section-title{\n108:     font-family:'Fraunces', serif; font-weight:400; font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.2vw,2.4rem);\n109:     letter-spacing:-0.01em; margin-bottom:14px;\n110:   }\n111:   .section-head-text h2.section-title{display:inline; margin-bottom:0;}\n112:   .section-desc{color:var(--ink-soft); font-size:1rem; line-height:1.6; max-width:560px;}\n113:   .section-head-text .section-desc{display:block; margin-top:10px;}\n114: \n115:   .about-section-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 280px; gap:64px; align-items:start;}\n116:   .frame{\n117:     position:relative; aspect-ratio:4/5; width:100%;\n118:     background:var(--panel);\n119:     border:1px solid var(--line);\n120:     display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;\n121:   }\n122:   .frame-initial{font-family:'Fraunces', serif; font-weight:400; font-size:5rem; color:var(--ink-soft);}\n123:   .frame-photo{position:absolute; inset:0; width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:contain; display:block;}\n124:   .frame-caption{\n125:     position:absolute; bottom:0; left:0; right:0;\n126:     border-top:1px solid var(--line); background:var(--paper);\n127:     padding:12px 14px; font-size:0.72rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.06em; text-transform:uppercase;\n128:     text-align:center; color:var(--ink-soft);\n129:   }\n130:   .about-copy p{font-size:1.02rem; line-height:1.75; color:var(--ink-soft); margin-bottom:18px;}\n131:   .about-copy p:first-child{font-size:1.12rem; color:var(--ink); font-weight:500;}\n132:   .skills-row{display:flex; gap:0; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-top:28px; border:1px solid var(--line);}\n133:   .skill-chip{\n134:     font-size:0.82rem; font-weight:600; padding:10px 18px;\n135:     border-right:1px solid var(--line); border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);\n136:   }\n137:   .skill-chip:last-child{border-right:none;}\n138: \n139:   .pin-grid{\n140:     display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(2, 1fr);\n141:     border:1px solid var(--line);\n142:   }\n143:   .pcard{\n144:     background:var(--paper);\n145:     display:flex; flex-direction:column;\n146:     border-right:1px solid var(--line);\n147:     border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);\n148:   }\n149:   .pcard:nth-child(2n){border-right:none;}\n150:   .pin-grid .pcard:nth-last-child(-n+2){border-bottom:none;}\n151: \n152:   .pcard-img-wrap{overflow:hidden; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}\n153:   .pcard-img{\n154:     width:100%; aspect-ratio:16/10; object-fit:cover; display:block;\n155:     filter:grayscale(8%);\n156:     transition:transform .5s ease;\n157:   }\n158:   .pcard:hover .pcard-img{transform:scale(1.03);}\n159: \n160:   .pcard-body{padding:32px 36px; flex:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column;}\n161:   .pcard-meta{font-size:0.74rem; font-weight:700; color:var(--accent); letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:10px;}\n162:   .pcard h3{\n163:     font-family:'Fraunces', serif; font-weight:400; font-size:1.45rem; margin-bottom:12px;\n164:   }\n165:   .pcard p{color:var(--ink-soft); font-size:0.96rem; line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:24px; flex:1;}\n166: \n167:   .btn{\n168:     display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px;\n169:     font-weight:600; font-size:0.84rem; letter-spacing:0.04em; text-transform:uppercase;\n170:     padding:13px 0; width:fit-content;\n171:     border-bottom:2px solid var(--ink); transition:border-color .2s, color .2s;\n172:   }\n173:   .btn:hover{color:var(--accent); border-color:var(--accent);}\n174:   .btn-block{\n175:     border:1px solid var(--ink); border-bottom-width:1px; padding:14px 26px; background:var(--ink); color:var(--paper);\n176:     transition:background .2s, color .2s, border-color .2s;\n177:   }\n178:   .btn-block:hover{background:var(--accent); border-color:var(--accent); color:#fff;}\n179: \n180:   .process-row{\n181:     display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);\n182:     border:1px solid var(--line);\n183:   }\n184:   .process-step{\n185:     padding:32px 28px; border-right:1px solid var(--line);\n186:   }\n187:   .process-step:last-child{border-right:none;}\n188:   .process-step .num{\n189:     font-family:'Fraunces', serif; font-style:italic; font-weight:400; font-size:1.3rem; color:var(--accent); margin-bottom:14px; display:block;\n190:   }\n191:   .process-step h4{font-size:0.98rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:10px;}\n192:   .process-step p{font-size:0.88rem; color:var(--ink-soft); line-height:1.55;}\n193: \n194:   #contact{border-bottom:none;}\n195:   .contact-grid{display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1px 1fr; gap:0;}\n196:   .contact-left{padding-right:56px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; justify-content:center;}\n197:   .contact-divider{background:var(--line);}\n198:   .contact-right{padding-left:56px; display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0; border:1px solid var(--line);}\n199:   .contact-row{\n200:     display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between;\n201:     padding:22px 28px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);\n202:   }\n203:   .contact-row:last-child{border-bottom:none;}\n204:   .contact-label{font-size:0.72rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--ink-soft);}\n205:   .contact-value{font-size:0.95rem; font-weight:600;}\n206:   .contact-row a.contact-value:hover{color:var(--accent);}\n207: \n208:   footer{\n209:     text-align:center; padding:28px 0; font-size:0.82rem; color:var(--ink-soft);\n210:   }\n211: \n212:   .reveal{opacity:0; transform:translateY(18px); transition:opacity .6s ease, transform .6s ease;}\n213:   .reveal.in{opacity:1; transform:translateY(0);}\n214: \n215:   @media (max-width:900px){\n216:     .hero-main{padding:60px 0 40px;}\n217:     .hero-stats{grid-template-columns:repeat(2, 1fr); row-gap:20px;}\n218:     .side-stat{border-right:none; border-bottom:1px solid var(--line); padding:0 0 20px;}\n219:     .side-stat:nth-child(odd){border-right:1px solid var(--line); padding-right:20px;}\n220:     .about-section-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:28px;}\n221:     .frame{width:140px; margin:0 auto;}\n222:     .pin-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}\n223:     .pcard{border-right:none !important;}\n224:     .process-row{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}\n225:     .process-step{border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}\n226:     .contact-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}\n227:     .contact-divider{display:none;}\n228:     .contact-right{padding-left:0; margin-top:36px;}\n229:     .contact-left{padding-right:0;}\n230:     .navlinks{display:none;}\n231:   }\n232: </style>\n233: </head>\n234: <body>\n235: \n236: <nav>\n237:   <div class=\"wrap\">\n238:     <a href=\"#\" class=\"brand\">Dhvani Chauhan<span>.</span></a>\n239:     <div class=\"navlinks\">\n240:       <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n241:       <a href=\"#work\">Work</a>\n242:       <a href=\"#process\">Process</a>\n243:       <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n244:       <a href=\"assets/Dhvani-Chauhan-Resume.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" class=\"nav-resume\">Resume</a>\n245:     </div>\n246:   </div>\n247: </nav>\n248: \n249: <header class=\"hero\">\n250:   <div class=\"wrap\">\n251:     <div class=\"hero-main\">\n252:       <h1 class=\"title\">Brand identity, packaging, and editorial design — built on <em>strategy and story</em>.</h1>\n253:       <p class=\"hero-sub\">Hi, my name is Dhvani Chauhan, and I am a Graphic Design student at Humber College. I am passionate about creating meaningful and visually engaging designs that connect with people. My interests include branding, packaging design, editorial design, and digital experiences. Through my work, I enjoy combining creativity with problem-solving to develop designs that are both functional and memorable. This portfolio showcases a selection of projects that reflect my skills, growth, and design journey as an emerging designer.</p>\n254:       <div class=\"hero-stats\">\n255:         <div class=\"side-stat\">\n256:           <span class=\"label\">Focus</span>\n257:           <span class=\"value\">Branding & Packaging</span>\n258:         </div>\n259:         <div class=\"side-stat\">\n260:           <span class=\"label\">Also</span>\n261:           <span class=\"value\">Editorial Design</span>\n262:         </div>\n263:         <div class=\"side-stat\">\n264:           <span class=\"label\">Based In</span>\n265:           <span class=\"value\">Toronto, Canada</span>\n266:         </div>\n267:         <div class=\"side-stat\">\n268:           <span class=\"label\">Available</span>\n269:           <span class=\"value\">Freelance & Full-time</span>\n270:         </div>\n271:       </div>\n272:     </div>\n273:   </div>\n274: </header>\n275: \n276: <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n277:   <div class=\"wrap\">\n278:     <div class=\"section-head\">\n279:       <span class=\"section-num reveal\">01</span>\n280:       <div class=\"section-head-text reveal\">\n281:         <h2 class=\"section-title\">About</h2>\n282:         <p class=\"section-desc\">A short introduction to who I am and how I work.</p>\n283:       </div>\n284:     </div>\n285:     <div class=\"about-section-grid\">\n286:       <div class=\"reveal about-copy\">\n287:         <p>I'm a Graphic Design student at Humber College with a focus on branding, packaging, and editorial design.</p>\n288:         <p>My work moves between brand identity, packaging systems, and editorial layout. I'm drawn to the detail that makes a brand feel like itself — a typeface choice, a colour decision, the way a label folds — and I build every project around a clear story, not just a clean surface.</p>\n289:         <div class=\"skills-row\">\n290:           <span class=\"skill-chip\">Brand Identity</span>\n291:           <span class=\"skill-chip\">Packaging Design</span>\n292:           <span class=\"skill-chip\">Editorial Layout</span>\n293:           <span class=\"skill-chip\">Photoshop</span>\n294:           <span class=\"skill-chip\">Illustrator</span>\n295:           <span class=\"skill-chip\">InDesign</span>\n296:         </div>\n297:       </div>\n298:       <div class=\"reveal frame\">\n299:         <img class=\"frame-photo\" src=\"assets/images/dhvani-photo.jpeg\" alt=\"Portrait of Dhvani Chauhan\">\n300:         <span class=\"frame-caption\">Humber College · Graphic Design</span>\n301:       </div>\n302:     </div>\n303:   </div>\n304: </section>\n305: \n306: <section id=\"work\" class=\"section\">\n307:   <div class=\"wrap\">\n308:     <div class=\"section-head\">\n309:       <span class=\"section-num reveal\">02</span>\n310:       <div class=\"section-head-text reveal\">\n311:         <h2 class=\"section-title\">Selected Work</h2>\n312:         <p class=\"section-desc\">A few projects spanning branding, packaging, and editorial design.</p>\n313:       </div>\n314:     </div>\n315: \n316:     <div class=\"pin-grid\">\n317: \n318:       <article class=\"pcard reveal\">\n319:         <div class=\"pcard-img-wrap\">\n320:           <img class=\"pcard-img\" src=\"assets/images/mockup for wine .jpg\" alt=\"From Soil to Soul wine branding campaign cover\">\n321:         </div>\n322:         <div class=\"pcard-body\">\n323:           <span class=\"pcard-meta\">Wine Branding Campaign</span>\n324:           <h3>From Soil to Soul & Valvet Roots label</h3>\n325:           <p>An editorial-driven wine brand campaign about place, people, and slow storytelling — built around earthy textures and a quiet colour story.</p>\n326:           <a class=\"btn\" href=\"project-from-soil-to-soul.html\">View Project →</a>\n327:         </div>\n328:       </article>\n329: \n330:       <article class=\"pcard reveal\">\n331:         <div class=\"pcard-img-wrap\">\n332:           <img class=\"pcard-img\" src=\"assets/images/rumour.Me .jpeg\" alt=\"RumourMe beauty brand campaign cover\">\n333:         </div>\n334:         <div class=\"pcard-body\">\n335:           <span class=\"pcard-meta\">Beauty Brand Campaign</span>\n336:           <h3>RumourMe</h3>\n337:           <p>A modern beauty brand built around confidence and self-expression, with bold type and visuals designed to hold attention.</p>\n338:           <a class=\"btn\" href=\"project-rumourme.html\">View Project →</a>\n339:         </div>\n340:       </article>\n341: \n342:       <article class=\"pcard reveal\">\n343:         <div class=\"pcard-img-wrap\">\n344:           <img class=\"pcard-img\" src=\"assets/images/Wine package.jpg\" alt=\"Velvet Roots wine packaging design cover\">\n345:         </div>\n346:         <div class=\"pcard-body\">\n347:           <span class=\"pcard-meta\">Wine Packaging Design</span>\n348:           <h3>Velvet Roots</h3>\n349:           <p>A wine packaging system designed to feel rich and tactile on the shelf, with label details that reward a second look.</p>\n350:           <a class=\"btn\" href=\"project-velvet-roots.html\">View Project →</a>\n351:         </div>\n352:       </article>\n353: \n354:       <article class=\"pcard reveal\">\n355:         <div class=\"pcard-img-wrap\">\n356:           <img class=\"pcard-img\" src=\"assets/images/movie mockup.jpeg\" alt=\"Enemies movie poster design cover\">\n357:         </div>\n358:         <div class=\"pcard-body\">\n359:           <span class=\"pcard-meta\">Movie Poster Design</span>\n360:           <h3>Enemies: A Tale for Lads and Lasses</h3>\n361:           <p>A movie poster concept balancing mood and narrative tension, using layered type and a restrained palette to set the tone.</p>\n362:           <a class=\"btn\" href=\"project-enemies.html\">View Project →</a>\n363:         </div>\n364:       </article>\n365: \n366:     </div>\n367:   </div>\n368: </section>\n369: \n370: <section id=\"process\" class=\"section\">\n371:   <div class=\"wrap\">\n372:     <div class=\"section-head\">\n373:       <span class=\"section-num reveal\">03</span>\n374:       <div class=\"section-head-text reveal\">\n375:         <h2 class=\"section-title\">Process</h2>\n376:         <p class=\"section-desc\">How a project moves from idea to finished design.</p>\n377:       </div>\n378:     </div>\n379:     <div class=\"process-row reveal\">\n380:       <div class=\"process-step\">\n381:         <span class=\"num\">i.</span>\n382:         <h4>Research & Story</h4>\n383:         <p>Understanding the brand's world before touching colour or type.</p>\n384:       </div>\n385:       <div class=\"process-step\">\n386:         <span class=\"num\">ii.</span>\n387:         <h4>Concept & Sketch</h4>\n388:         <p>Loose exploration of type, mood, and palette before anything is final.</p>\n389:       </div>\n390:       <div class=\"process-step\">\n391:         <span class=\"num\">iii.</span>\n392:         <h4>Design & Refine</h4>\n393:         <p>Building the system in Illustrator, Photoshop, and InDesign.</p>\n394:       </div>\n395:       <div class=\"process-step\">\n396:         <span class=\"num\">iv.</span>\n397:         <h4>Polish & Present</h4>\n398:         <p>Tightening detail until the final result feels effortless.</p>\n399:       </div>\n400:     </div>\n\n(Showing lines 1-400 of 447. Use offset=401 to continue.)\n</content>",
